item.title: Dashboard Traffic Alert in West Java
item.description: This analytics dashboard shows the proportion of traffic alerts in the city and street of West Java. The local government can use the dashboard to monitor and get insight into their area's traffic condition.

item.title: COVID-19 Indonesia Dashboard
